('Grammar and Structure', 'Verb Form', 'be extended', 'They requested that the deadline _________ .', 'be extended', 'is extended', 'extends', 'has extended', 'Subjunctive mood after \"requested\". Base verb form.'),
('Grammar and Structure', 'Verb Form', 'Having reviewed', '_________ the evidence, the jury acquitted the defendant.', 'Having reviewed', 'Reviewing', 'Reviewed', 'To review', 'Perfect participle shows prior completed action.'),
('Grammar and Structure', 'Verb Form', 'be', 'It is crucial that all data _________ verified.', 'be', 'is', 'was', 'has been', 'Subjunctive after \"crucial\". Base verb form.'),
